Welcome to Rockhampton

SIGNATURE ON THE ROCKS

From the developers of Grenadines Resort, Katampe, one of Nigeria’s finest residential communities, is a well-nested fully inhabited private estate that has become a unique centerpiece of art within the Abuja geographical enclave.

We are excited to share our newest residential community – Rockhampton by Grenadines Homes, a blend of nature, innovation, and functionality, put together to make an exquisite mountainside community.

DOWNLOAD BROCHURE

ESCAPE THE CONGESTION, EXPERIENCE TRANQUILITY

A well-crafted and sustainable housing solution to the high demand for shelters in the capital city, Abuja.

The Rockhampton is situated in Katampe extension, with easy access to town, proximity to major landmarks, and other recreational facilities like the IBB Golf Course. The Rockhampton provides an escape from the bustle of town just a few minutes away.

NATURE . INNOVATION . FUNCTIONALITY

Deliberately planned for sustainability and functionality birthed with innovation, the design includes 4 Bedroom Pent Apartments, 3 Bedroom Luxury Condos, 4 Bedroom Terrace Apartments, and 4 Bedroom Semi Detached Luxury Villas, all designed to provide maximum comfort, the highest level of luxury, and unique recreational facilities to the environment at large.

3 BEDROOM LUXURY CONDOS

Rockhampton by Grenadines design comprises of 4 Bedroom Pent Apartments, 3 Bedroom Luxury Condos, 4 Bedroom Terrace Apartments, and 4 Bedroom Semi Detached Luxury Villas. With see thru kitchen, family lounge, party deck, and spectacular balcony view of Katampe, Abuja.
A unit of Rockhampton is a luxury home with maids’ room, bedrooms with walk-in closers, anteroom, and spacious living areas (all rooms en-suite).
All units are fitted with exclusive elevator, terrace garden and other appliances.

ABUJA

CENTRE OF UNITY

The Federal Capital Territory of Nigeria, Abuja is one of the foremost destinations for large multinationals, affluent Nigerians and the power seat of the country. Abuja is well developed and offers the best in luxury and comfort to every Nigerian as well as visitors to the country.
